- cs.AR (Hardware Architecture) is relevant as the paper specifically mentions the Intel Skylake and Nvidia V100 architectures.
- cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science) is relevant as the paper deals with molecular dynamics simulations, which fall under the category of computational science.
- cs.NA (Numerical Analysis) is relevant as the paper discusses accuracy and optimization of a numerical code.
